  <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
  
  <p>Peprime is aware that you care how information about you is used and shared and hence appreciate your trust in us to do that carefully and sensibly. This policy describes the privacy policy of Peprime.com. By visiting Peprime.com, you are accepting and consenting to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.                                      The information we gather from customers helps us to continually improve the service at Peprime.com. We use the information to handle orders, deliver products and services, process payments, communicate with you about orders, products, services and promotional offers, update our records and generally maintain your accounts with us, display content such as customer reviews and recommend merchandise and services that might be of interest to you. We also use this information to improve our store and website, prevent or detect fraud or abuses of our website and enable third parties to carry out technical, logistical or other functions on our behalf.     <br>                            
    <br>
    <strong>(a) Commitment to Data Security and Distribution of Information</strong><br><br>

    Information about our customers is an important part of our business and we are not in the business of selling it to others. Peprime is earnestly committed to data security of our customers hence customer information is kept secure to the extent reasonably practicable. We work to protect the security of our customer information during transmission by using Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) software, which encrypts information you input. We reveal only the last four digits of credit card numbers when confirming an order. As standard practice we transmit the entire credit card number to the appropriate credit card company during order processing. To ensure that we maintain high security procedures we may request proof of identity before we disclose personal information to you. Please note that it is important for you to protect against unauthorised access to your password and to your computer. Make sure that you sign off when you finish using a shared computer. 
    <br>Only authorized employees, affiliates and third party service providers (who have agreed to keep information secure and confidential as permitted by the applicable laws on data protection) have access to this information. All emails and newsletters from Peprime.com website allow you to opt out of further mailings. 
    <br>We work closely with affiliated/third party businesses which we do not control. In some cases, these businesses operate stores at Peprime.com or sell offerings to you at Peprime.com. Our website may include third party advertising and links to other Websites. We do not provide any personally identifiable customer information to these advertisers or third-party websites. These third party websites and advertisers, or internet advertising companies working on their behalf, sometimes use technology to send the advertisements that appear on our website directly to your browser. They automatically receive your IP address when this happens. They may also use cookies and other tracking technologies to measure the effectiveness of their ads and to enhance advertising content. We do not have access to or control over cookies or other features that third party or affiliates may use, and the information practices of these advertisers and third party websites are not covered by this Privacy Policy. Please contact them directly for more information about their Privacy Policies and Term of Services. 
    <br>We release account and other personal information when we believe release is appropriate to comply with the law; enforce or apply our Terms of Service and other agreements; or protect the rights, property or safety of Peprime.com, our users or others. We often employ third party, contractors, other companies and individuals to perform functions on our behalf, such as fulfilling orders, delivering packages, sending postal mail and e-mail, providing marketing assistance, processing credit card payments and providing customer service. They have access to personal information needed to perform their functions, but may not use it for other purposes. Further, they must process the personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy and as permitted by the United Kingdom's Data Protection Act.
    <br>Whenever we transfer personal information to countries outside of the European Economic Area in the course of sharing information as set out above, we will ensure that the information is transferred in accordance with this Privacy Policy and as permitted by the applicable laws on data protection. We may include the information you provide in the stories we publish on our website. We may also use your name and photograph when you express your views on certain topic(s). However, we would also observe anonymity when you request for it.
    <br>
    <br>
    <strong>(b) Cookies and Tracking Technology
    </strong><br><br>
    The Website may use cookies and tracking technology for gathering information such as browser type and operating system, tracking the number of visitors to the website, and understanding how visitors use the website. Cookies can also help customise the website for visitors. Cookies allow you to take advantage of some of Peprime.com's essential features and we recommend that you leave them turned on. Note that if you block or otherwise reject our cookies, you will not be able to add items to your Shopping Cart, proceed to Checkout, or use any Peprime.com products and services that require you to Sign in. However, if you do leave cookies turned on, be sure to sign off when you finish using a shared computer.
    <br><br>
    <strong>(c) Privacy Contact Information and Revisions</strong><br><br>

    If you have any concerns, questions or comments about Privacy Policy at Peprime.com, please e-mail: info@peprime.com a thorough description and we will try to resolve the issue.
    <br>Our business changes constantly and our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service will also change. We reserve the right to make changes to this policy. Any changes to this policy will be posted.<br></p> 
   

